# Wiring NodeMCU ESP8266

## Pin Mapping
- D1 (GPIO5) -> I2C SCL
- D2 (GPIO4) -> I2C SDA
- D6 (GPIO12) -> Relay control (via resistor basis ke NPN)

## I2C
- DS3231 dan LCD1602 I2C bisa satu bus (paralel SDA/SCL).
- Gunakan level shifter jika sisi LCD berjalan di 5V.

## Relay Driver (NPN)
- D6 -> R1 1k -> basis NPN
- Basis -> R2 10k -> GND (pulldown)
- Emitter -> GND
- Collector -> salah satu kaki coil relay
- Kaki coil relay lain -> +5V
- Dioda flyback paralel coil:
  - Anoda ke sisi collector
  - Katoda ke +5V

## Supply
- +5V untuk VIN NodeMCU, relay coil, LCD (jika perlu 5V)
- GND semua modul wajib common ground
